quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  21,30,"Ingaba abo bangakholwayo abaqondi na ukuba amazulu nomhlaba ayedityanisiwe eyinto enye. Saza Thina Sawahlukanisa, Senza yonke into ephilayo ngamanzi, kanti abakholwa na"
  21,31,"Kananjalo Sibeke emhlabeni iintaba eziqinileyo, kuba hleze (umhlaba) uphephuke nabo. Saza Sabeka apho iindlela ezinkulu ekugqithwa ngazo khon’ukuze bakhokeleleke"
  21,32,"Ke kaloku Senza isibhakabhaka saba luphahla olukhuselekileyo, kodwa bona, kwimiqondiso yaso bayatshikila bafulathele"
  21,33,"Yaye nguYe Odale ubusuku nemini, nelanga nenyanga, nganye kuzo ijikeleza kwisijikelezisi sayo"
  21,34,Kananjalo aSizanga senze namnye kubantu ukuba angafi ngaphambili kunawe (wena Muhammad). Ingaba usakufa wena baza kuphila ngonaphakade bona
  21,35,"Wonke umntu uza kukungcamla ukufa, kananjalo Siya kwenza uvavanyo kuni ngokungendawo nangokulungileyo. Ukanti kuThi kulapho (niza) kubuyela khona"
  21,36,"Ke bona abo bangakholwayo xa bekubona, (Muhammad) abakuthatheli ntweni ngaphandle kokukugxeka, (besithi): “Ingaba lo ngulowo ukhankanya oothixo benu?” Ukanti bona xa kukhankanywa uSozinceba, abakholwa"
  21,37,"Umntu wadalwa waba sisingxami, (wangabi namonde). Ndiza kunibonisa ke imiqondiso yaM (impindezelo), ningaNdiceli ngokungxama"
  21,38,"Kananjalo bathi: “Siya kuba nini na esi sithembiso, ukuba nithetha inyaniso?”"
  21,39,Akwaba abo bangakholwayo bebelazi ixesha abangayi kukwazi ngalo ukubuyisa umva uMlilo ebusweni babo okanye emiqolo yabo kwanokuba abayi kuncedwa nakuncedwa
  21,40,"Ukusuka apho liya kubafikela bengalindelanga libamangalise, yaye abayi kukwazi ukulishenxisa, bengayi kumelwa nakumelwa"
  21,41,Inene abaThunywa (abaninzi) bagculelwa ngaphambi kwakho (wena Muhammad) kodwa abagculeli (abo) baye barhangqelwa ngoko kugculela kwabo